        <div>
          <strong>Nx</strong>
          <p>Managing monorepos with smart builds, caching, and code generation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Why "Orcine"?</h2>
    <p>
      The name Orcine is a tribute to my mother — the most loving and inspiring person in my life. ❤️
      She's the reason I keep building, keep learning, and keep pushing forward. 
      Naming this project after her is my way of carrying her spirit into everything I create.
    </p>

    <h2>Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
      I believe in shipping early, iterating fast, and writing code that's easy to reason about.
      Good software is built on pragmatic decisions, not hype cycles. I favour tools that
      respect developer time and scale without drama.
    </p>

    <h2>Connect</h2>
    <ul class="connect-list">
      <li><a href="https://github.com/orcinebv" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub — @orcinebv</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/patric_slagveer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter — @patric_slagveer</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-hero picture {
    display: block;
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 3px solid var(--border);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-avatar {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about-hero {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-hero picture {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
    }
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .about p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .tech-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .tech-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .tech-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .tech-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
    border-radius: 0;
    border: none;
  }

  .tech-card strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .tech-card p {
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .connect-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .connect-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .connect-list a {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
</style>
